Ashes
Australia Men's team will begin their Ashes title defence with the first of the five Tests at the Gabba in Brisbane from December 8 in a bumper summer schedule announced by Cricket Australia on Wednesday. The national women's team, too, begin their quest for a third consecutive defence of the trophy in an across-formats series beginning with the one-off Test at the Manuka Oval in the Australian capital from January 27.
